sources.description:
Four highly skilled pilots are accepted into an elite military training center and trained by the legendary Commander Kemal. He is one of the strictest instructors, preparing them for the difficult military life they are becoming part of. When the four pilots have an opportunity to participate at the "Anatolian Eagles," an international training camp, they realize that everything that Commander Kemal has been teaching them has led to this moment.
